{
  "name": "ColorStop",
  "summary": "<p><strong>ColorStop</strong> 对象可用来设置单元格填充属性，包括 <strong>Color</strong>、<strong>ThemeColor</strong> 和 <strong>TintAndShade</strong> 属性。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*以下示例演示如何对 ColorStop 对象应用属性。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternLinearGradient\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Degree</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">135</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStops1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    colorStops1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorDark1\n    colorStops1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStops2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>)\n    colorStops2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent1\n    colorStops2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStops3 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStops3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorDark1\n    colorStops3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示当前选定区域的第一个ColorStop对象的位置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Position</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>表示某一区域或选定内容中渐变填充的光圈点。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表 ET 应用程序的 <strong>Application</strong>对象。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表指定对象的创建程序的 <strong>Application</strong>对象（可对一个 OLE 自动化对象使用该属性来返回该对象的应用程序）。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Color",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定对象的颜色。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动单元格的第二个ColorStop对象颜色是否为蓝色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> == <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将当前选定区域的第一个ColorStop对象的颜色设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。Creator 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Position",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置 <strong>ColorStop</strong> 对象的位置。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动单元格的第二个ColorStop对象的位置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Position</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将当前选定区域的第一个ColorStop对象的位置设置为0.8。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Position</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.8</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（double 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ThemeColor",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定对象的主颜色。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*对当前选定内容应用主题颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent1\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动单元格第三个ColorStop对象的主题颜色是否为 xlThemeColorDark1。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> == xlThemeColorDark1)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "TintAndShade",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定对象的淡色和阴影。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*对当前选定内容应用淡色和阴影。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent1\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动单元格第二个ColorStop对象的TintAndShade属性是否为1。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除指定对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动单元格的第一个ColorStop对象删除。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将当前选定区域的第二个ColorStop对象删除。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "<p>void</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}